From c54572e1160ba54a8b1739986c842b9a43cb01ba Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Wanming Hu <huwanming@huawei.com>
Date: Sat, 13 Sep 2025 18:15:48 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] xenvm: support mcs rpmsg communication

Support mcs rpmsg communication, by using xenstore
to fetch gnttab reference and evtchn port from master.
Then we initialize shared memory and interrupt through
them, and initialize the rpmsg device and services.

Signed-off-by: Wanming Hu <huwanming@huawei.com>
---
